  "detailed_description": "<i> \"If the devil gave man free will, let him be the origin of all evil in man's deeds, let him be blamed instead of the stupid man, who does as his lowest urges and desires command.\"</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/426050/extras/cfa8bda681788bd42a5d35a65553da1b.avif?t=1724973754\" width=177 height=126 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tA hybrid of adventure game and classic grid-based dungeon crawler, set in the medieval Czech town of Jilemnice and its hilly surroundings.<br></li><li>\tA dark story about an innkeeper, beer and the devil.<br></li><li>\tPoetic dialogues, wise words, bargaining, fights...<br></li><li>\tAn RPG without magic, elves or hobbits... (we're in Jilemnice after all)<br></li><li>\tNo saving the world, no heroism.<br></li><li>\tLow hardware requirements.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/426050/extras/e12fbe807a724ed67cd7dba6b54b7dc2.avif?t=1724973754\" width=177 height=126 /></span><br>The game has been released on Steam on its 10th anniversary<br></li><li>\tWindows 10 compatibility<br></li><li>\tSteam achievements<br></li><li>\tMinor fixes and adjustments</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<i> \"If the devil gave man free will, let him be the origin of all evil in man's deeds, let him be blamed instead of the stupid man, who does as his lowest urges and desires command.\"</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/426050/extras/cfa8bda681788bd42a5d35a65553da1b.avif?t=1724973754\" width=177 height=126 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tA hybrid of adventure game and classic grid-based dungeon crawler, set in the medieval Czech town of Jilemnice and its hilly surroundings.<br></li><li>\tA dark story about an innkeeper, beer and the devil.<br></li><li>\tPoetic dialogues, wise words, bargaining, fights...<br></li><li>\tAn RPG without magic, elves or hobbits... (we're in Jilemnice after all)<br></li><li>\tNo saving the world, no heroism.<br></li><li>\tLow hardware requirements.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/426050/extras/e12fbe807a724ed67cd7dba6b54b7dc2.avif?t=1724973754\" width=177 height=126 /></span><br>The game has been released on Steam on its 10th anniversary<br></li><li>\tWindows 10 compatibility<br></li><li>\tSteam achievements<br></li><li>\tMinor fixes and adjustments</li></ul>",
